name: Send a Dog a Bone
overview:
Where we send rawhide dog bones through the mail wrapped in a personalized message for that special someone in your life.

Dogs are an important part of our lives. Sending them a bone is a great way to share all the special times in your life with them. You can send a bone for a Birthday, Christmas or Valentines gift. Send one as a congratulations on the new puppies, get well soon after a surgery or a just thinking about you bone. What better way to impress the cute girl down the street than by sending her dog a bone. The list of reasons in endless, and the bottom line is, you donâ€™t need a special holiday to send a dog a bone. Whatever the occasion, we bet you know of a dog that deserves one!
